# Venture Canvas Template

> A streamlined business model canvas for evaluating new venture ideas.

---

## How to Use

1. Copy this template for each new venture idea
2. Fill in sections as you develop the concept
3. Use "?" for unknowns that need research
4. Mark sections as "TBD" if not yet considered
5. Review and iterate as the concept evolves

